data.title: Spanish President to Visit Washington in May
data.text:
Jose Maria Aznar and Mrs. Aznar to visit Camp David on May 3-4

The President and Mrs. Bush will welcome Spanish President Jose Maria Aznar and Mrs. Aznar for a visit to Camp David on May 3-4, according to the following White House announcement:

The White House

Office of the Press Secretary April 19, 2002

Statement by the Press Secretary

Spanish President to Visit Washington

The President and Mrs. Bush will welcome Spanish President Jose Maria Aznar and Mrs. Aznar for a visit to Camp David on May 3-4. The United States and Spain enjoy a close relationship and the United States appreciates Spain's steadfast support in the war on terrorism.
